<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201120/091d6e95425b4b53824cd9a3edf84a5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>等级共享，战斗女团即刻成型！</strong></p>
